    - Now puts up a pop-up at take or include reporting on not taken or locked out nodes.


27-03-2008 Release Notes for FwFsm v25r24
    - DIM v17r3
    - SMI++ v32r6
    - PVSS 3.6 (only)
    - Linux executables built on: SLC4 with gcc 3.4.6

Bug Fixes/Improvements:
